    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "because it's above the router, the first `app.get()` (or other) calls `use(app.router)` so in that case you want:\n\n``` js\napp.configure(function() {\n  app.use(app.router):\n  app.use(express.static(__dirname));\n});\n```\n\nto give it precedence\n",
